name: À l'aube | Les idées mortes
description:
"À l'aube" is the dawn, the beautiful sunrise at the beach of the abandoned, dead ideas. It opens the new collection of images entitled "Les idées mortes".

"Les idées mortes" is a series of experiments, ideas, sketches and studies that never developed into standalone pieces, but are beautiful little trinkets nonetheless. Who knows, there may be a real gem lost among them.
